{"tid":2334643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年中秋違宵禁令還柙已兩個半月 辯方再度申請保釋終獲羅德泉批准","createTime":"2020-12-21T09:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T11:30:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d40c3abba8d7ffa02bc4d9e389380f94f0f81469","tid":2334643,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日有網民發起「三罷」，多區發生衝突，其間兩名年青年涉在旺角管有雷射筆及伸縮棍，被控管有適合作非法用途工具罪 。案件今在西九龍裁判法院審前覆核，辯方為其中一名早前因在中秋翌日違反宵禁保釋條件、因而被取消擔保的青年再次申請保釋，指被告已經知錯及反省，加上今晚是冬至，明天更是被告生日，希望法庭給予機會，讓被告保釋候審。主任裁判官羅德泉考慮後批准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案件今日進行審前覆核，法庭將案件訂於明年4月7日審訊。本案兩名被告原本均獲保釋，但次被告因今年中秋翌日被發現違反宵禁的保釋條件，因而被取消擔保，還柙至今已兩個半月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今日再次為郭申請保釋，並呈上由被告、其母及跟進社工撰寫的信件。辯方大狀指，被告已深深明白自己沒有珍惜法庭給予的機會，今年中秋翌日因一時貪玩，與朋友到朋友家的天台玩樂，其後被警方截查，揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n被告遭還柙的兩個半月內有讀書，在羈留所內體會到可以在外面讀書的機會得來不易，亦想向法庭道歉，「好對唔住法庭，佢完全明白因一時貪玩，而招來呢兩個幾月，係佢自己嘅過錯」。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官羅德泉考慮後，批准次被告以早前原有條件保釋，即須守宵禁令、禁足令及每周向警署報到一次等條件。羅官批准保釋後嚴詞警告被告，要求被告嚴格遵守並且嚴肅對待所有保釋條件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/AJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FAJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=49c738a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FAJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ%2F&h=5803cdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/AJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a8226a8ccdb29fec69f74214cc03a217ebfba017","tid":2334643,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a17ca2b2d34a13869529834c5d2d9ce93550ed","tid":2334643,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ec0a8d824e0ebbcfd32f82c74b65c07bc7eae7","tid":2334643,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7107408b616818f0b333562976c432e67886a6a2","tid":2334643,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"羅官又要俾班藍屍屌啦"},{"pid":"923d537faf080ecfb46ac5aef76e9bf66b70c46d","tid":2334643,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"辯方大狀代表被告多次向法庭致歉，並指今晚是冬至，而明天是被告生日，加上審訊排到明年4月，如果繼續將被告還柙，<span class=\"red\">他接受審訊時將會已經還柙超過6個月。</span>"},{"pid":"74b13de922fcf800363e0322425bbd689b495e3d","tid":2334643,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50161fcc95bc8e847f9335f3320b16cf0ada7477","tid":2334643,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bb404885eabae5514a8c6fd9d9fcf570c0426d","tid":2334643,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7589d98c57ed2173a2437efeed874dc2a22acf96","tid":2334643,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:30:42.000Z